But those descriptions usually don't matter when it's Texas vs OU at the State Fair in Dallas.  //kvue.tv/1RAA3k2   Mike Barnes reports on Texas' win over OU KVUE/AP 11:33 p.m. CDT October 10, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
The Sooners were in the top ten. The Longhorns were unranked and double digit underdogs. 
But those descriptions usually don't matter when it's Texas vs OU at the State Fair in Dallas. 
Charlie Strong gets perhaps the biggest win of his tenure at UT, upsetting Oklahoma 24-17. 
KVUE's Mike Barnes has more from Dallas. Mike Barnes reports from Texas-OU KVUE Read or Share this story: http://kvue.tv/1RAA3k2 TOP VIDEOS
